column2:
"*Sigh*
It took a while to get back."

"Geez, Elder really did it.
Oh well, at least he's gone."

"Yup, now that he's gone,
we don't need to think about it."

"Now that you mention it, those ARKS that keep coming
are starting to get on my nerves."

"They're soo annoying that
I want to eat them already."

"
The Matter Board [History that holds the darkness] has been received.
"
